653        Objects.requireNonNull(currency, CartDraft.class + ": currency is missing");
654        return new CartDraftImpl(currency, key, customerId, customerEmail, customerGroup, anonymousId, store, country,
655            inventoryMode, taxMode, taxRoundingMode, taxCalculationMode, lineItems, customLineItems, shippingAddress,
656            billingAddress, shippingMethod, externalTaxRateForShippingMethod, custom, locale,
657            deleteDaysAfterLastModification, origin, shippingRateInput, itemShippingAddresses, discountCodes);
658    }
659
660    /**
661     * builds CartDraft without checking for non null required values
662     */
663    public CartDraft buildUnchecked() {
664        return new CartDraftImpl(currency, key, customerId, customerEmail, customerGroup, anonymousId, store, country,
665            inventoryMode, taxMode, taxRoundingMode, taxCalculationMode, lineItems, customLineItems, shippingAddress,
666            billingAddress, shippingMethod, externalTaxRateForShippingMethod, custom, locale,
667            deleteDaysAfterLastModification, origin, shippingRateInput, itemShippingAddresses, discountCodes);
668    }

670    public static CartDraftBuilder of() {
671        return new CartDraftBuilder();
672    }

674    public static CartDraftBuilder of(final CartDraft template) {
675        CartDraftBuilder builder = new CartDraftBuilder();
676        builder.currency = template.getCurrency();
677        builder.key = template.getKey();
678        builder.customerId = template.getCustomerId();
679        builder.customerEmail = template.getCustomerEmail();
680        builder.customerGroup = template.getCustomerGroup();
681        builder.anonymousId = template.getAnonymousId();
682        builder.store = template.getStore();
683        builder.country = template.getCountry();
684        builder.inventoryMode = template.getInventoryMode();
685        builder.taxMode = template.getTaxMode();
686        builder.taxRoundingMode = template.getTaxRoundingMode();
687        builder.taxCalculationMode = template.getTaxCalculationMode();
688        builder.lineItems = template.getLineItems();
689        builder.customLineItems = template.getCustomLineItems();
690        builder.shippingAddress = template.getShippingAddress();
691        builder.billingAddress = template.getBillingAddress();
692        builder.shippingMethod = template.getShippingMethod();
693        builder.externalTaxRateForShippingMethod = template.getExternalTaxRateForShippingMethod();
694        builder.custom = template.getCustom();
695        builder.locale = template.getLocale();
696        builder.deleteDaysAfterLastModification = template.getDeleteDaysAfterLastModification();
697        builder.origin = template.getOrigin();
698        builder.shippingRateInput = template.getShippingRateInput();
699        builder.itemShippingAddresses = template.getItemShippingAddresses();
700        builder.discountCodes = template.getDiscountCodes();
701        return builder;
702    }
